    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="搜索功能：-algolia，"><a href="#搜索功能：-algolia，" class="headerlink" title="搜索功能： algolia，"></a>搜索功能： algolia，</h2><blockquote><p>参考了 <a href="https://juejin.im/post/5af3f9d1518825673e35a6eb" title="https://juejin.im/post/5af3f9d1518825673e35a6eb" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo+Next集成Algolia搜索</a></p></blockquote><a id="more"></a><h2 id="评论功能：-Gitalk"><a href="#评论功能：-Gitalk" class="headerlink" title="评论功能： Gitalk"></a>评论功能： Gitalk</h2><h2 id="文章阅读统计：-leancloud"><a href="#文章阅读统计：-leancloud" class="headerlink" title="文章阅读统计： leancloud"></a>文章阅读统计： leancloud</h2><h2 id="添加-RSS"><a href="#添加-RSS" class="headerlink" title="添加 RSS"></a>添加 RSS</h2><blockquote><p>参考自 <a href="https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000009544924" title="https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000009544924" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo的next主题个性化配置教程</a></p></blockquote><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/10/18/5bc877472fd9e.png" alt="微信图片_20181018200542.png"></p><p>首先，切换到根目录，安装 Hexo 插件 hexo-generator-feed：（会保存在 <code>node_modules</code> 文件夹）<br><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span> npm install --save hexo-generator-feed</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>接下来，进入根目录下的 <code>_config.yml</code> 文件，<strong>添加</strong>：<br><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span> Extensions</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># Plugins: http://hexo.io/plugins/</span><br><span class="line">plugins: hexo-generate-feed</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>然后，进入 themes/next 目录下的 <code>_config.yml</code> 文件，<strong>修改</strong>：<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Set rss to false to disable feed link.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Leave rss as empty to use site's feed link.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Set rss to specific value if you have burned your feed already.</span></span><br><span class="line">rss: /atom.xml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>配置完成后，重新生成一次（会在 ./public 文件夹中看到 atom.xml 文件）<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><hr><p><strong>其它优化参考：</strong></p><ol><li><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/33616481" title="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/33616481" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo搭建的GitHub博客之优化大全</a></li></ol>]]></content>
    
